originalText.text: Minus the switch up of the policies, charges and method of pay, storing here has been pretty amazing for the most part. I cannot complain much. Ever since I first started storing here, all of the employees, cleaners/porters and especially the manager have been great to me. Darrell, Juan, Arne and Keyonna have been excellent to me during my time here. I highly appreciate this company and especially the staff at this location.

originalText.text: I needed to rent a storage unit this weekend and Allen and the team here at the 107th street location were great!!!  They were super helpful and very patient, and I was very grateful for their help. This location is also extremely clean and easy to move around in, I highly recommend!!

originalText.text: Just started my lease but I've helped a friend move into various units here for years.The staff is SUPER friendly, thorough and helpful, which is why I decided to come back here when it was time for me to rent a unit myself. Thanks Arné, Juan, and the person who I cannot remember his name but was very funny that was there back in Oct '23!

I’m not usually one to write a review. But, as a long time customer in your facility (west 107th street) I wanted to commend Arne and Keyunna!   They helped me with a difficult situation with Grace, Professionalism, Kindness and Respect!  In a time where every penny counts they were able to help make a difficult situation into an amazing experience.

Thank you!!
Selma Winston

originalText.text:
We recently had the pleasure of dealing with Arné at Manhattan Mini Storage on the UWS while in search of a new storage unit, and I feel compelled to share the exceptional experience. From the moment we walked in, Arné greeted us with a warmth and professionalism that instantly put us at ease. Understanding our needs and constraints, he went above and beyond, demonstrating an impressive knowledge of the facility's options and providing us with tailored solutions that exceeded our expectations.

Arné's attentiveness did not just stop at finding us the right unit; he also ensured that the entire process was smooth and hassle-free. He took the time to explain all the paperwork in detail, answered every question we had with patience and clarity, and even followed up with us after we had moved our belongings in to ensure everything was to our satisfaction. His dedication to customer service was truly remarkable.

But what stood out most was Arné's genuine care for the customers. He made us feel valued and respected, turning what could have been a stressful task into a pleasant experience. It's rare to encounter someone so committed to excellence in service and it's clear that Arné is a significant asset to Manhattan Mini Storage.

Thank you, Arné, for making our storage unit search not just successful, but enjoyable. Your hard work and dedication did not go unnoticed, and we look forward to dealing with you again in the future. Manhattan Mini Storage is lucky to have you on their team!
